text: I was on OkCupid and I got this message
from this guy he said I am a houseboy I
like to serve strong confident women I
asked for nothing in return I also like
women who smoke he even in one text said
let me be your pig slave ashtray you
don't want to be a maid he wanted to be
subjugated and feel like he was working
for this woman who was better than him I
spoke to a friend about it and he said
you have to respond to this guy so I
messaged him back I could work with it
he gets what he wants you know I could
like throw coffee grounds in his face or
something I get what I want which is a
clean apartment we had been texting back
and forth for a little while and he had
flaked on me twice I realized this man
was never going to come clean my
apartment mmm then I really needed to go
to Ikea I got in touch when I said it's
your lucky day
you can be my chauffeur so we set a date
if I was getting the free ride to Ikea I
should give something to him too
he wanted to serve this strong confident
woman I wanted to give him that I called
him and I was like where are you
said I'm on my way I'm on my way I'm in
traffic said okay where are you I was
trying to muster as much attitude and
unpleasantness as I could I got in the
car and the first thing he said to me
was oh you're really pretty I was just
like yeah okay thanks like still trying
to be this domineering tough woman right
so we started talking we talked about
the situation in Israel and he had a
surprisingly nuanced to take on the
situation he was up on the news he
shared his own opinions it was basically
just this really interesting
conversation with a smart guy we did our

get to my street and I say okay bye
thank you he looks at me and he says you
know what you seem really nice and then
he walked away and I thought to myself
is that really a compliment coming from
this guy who wants to be abused and
degraded by a strong woman what he was
telling me was basically that I entirely
failed at playing the role I was trying
to play
